    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved. Whether you\u2019re commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to hit the road with you! Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
